29 Ask Peter for more information about the house
28 Get up and run

With authority in your voice, you demand, "Who are you? Where am I?" The man quickly and urgently responds, "I am Peter Vilkas, I live in the next village and I am on my way home. You are not safe here. You must come with me if you hope to live. The residents of the House on the Hill will soon realise that you are missing and they won't rest until you are recaptured." 
What next?